{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"6cb530b1-a984-488c-a845-cabc872e3654","content":"Here's what breaks in each case and the fixes:\n\n---\n\n### 1. `Buffer.cs` — `InlineArray` on `record struct` is now an error\n\nC# 13 forbids `[InlineArray]` on `record struct` types (they synthesize equality members that access beyond `_element0`, which is invalid for inline arrays).\n\n**Fix:** Change `record struct` → plain `struct`:\n\n```csharp\n[System.Runtime.CompilerServices.InlineArray(10)]\nstruct Buffer\n{\n    private int _element0;\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### 2. `Generator.cs` — `unsafe` no longer flows into local functions in iterators\n\nC# 13 stopped propagating the `unsafe` context from the enclosing class/method into local functions within iterator methods. The `stackalloc` in `Process()` no longer inherits `unsafe`.\n\n**Fix:** Mark the local function itself `unsafe`:\n\n```csharp\nclass DataGenerator\n{\n    IEnumerable<int> Generate()\n    {\n        yield return 1;\n        Process();\n        unsafe void Process()\n        {\n            int* p = stackalloc int[10];\n        }\n    }\n}\n```\n\n(The `unsafe` on the class is no longer needed unless used elsewhere.)\n\n---\n\n### 3. `Resolver.cs` — Collection expression `[]` is now ambiguous\n\nC# 13 improved collection expression conversions to span types. Now `[]` converts to **both** `ReadOnlySpan<int>` and `Span<object>`, making the call ambiguous (neither overload is \"better\").\n\n**Fix:** Disambiguate with an explicit type:\n\n```csharp\nstatic void Main()\n{\n    Process(ReadOnlySpan<int>.Empty);\n    // or: Process((ReadOnlySpan<int>)[]);\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n| File | Breaking change | Fix |\n|------|----------------|-----|\n| `Buffer.cs` | `InlineArray` banned on `record struct` | Use plain `struct` |\n| `Generator.cs` | `unsafe` doesn't flow into iterator local functions | Add `unsafe` to the local function |\n| `Resolver.cs` | `[]` now converts to multiple span types → ambiguity | Explicitly specify the target type |","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"6bed82c3-352c-44c1-84ac-0c2813322cc4","outputTokens":545},"id":"7cffaa96-d362-4cab-ac7f-419c23523a72","timestamp":"2026-04-08T01:11:02.194Z","parentId":"9177bd0f-38e2-4f05-a25c-d74bc31334e8"}
